overview:
Florida ETR is a leading DMV-certified provider of temp tag and electronic temporary registration services to automotive dealerships based in Florida. The company became a DMV certified ETR vendor in 2008 when the state of Florida passed legislation changing the way dealers issued temp tags.

Their internet based program serves independent and franchise car dealers throughout the entire state of Florida and allows temp tags and temporary registation forms to be printed at the time of sale in literally just a couple steps. The company has seen rapid growth since the introduction of its integrated dealer software programs and is often recognized for having top-notch customer service.

Users of their award winning dealer management system, Advanced Car Dealer Manager, get the added benefit of virtually automated temp tag printing. Advanced Car Dealer Manager first came on the market in 2003 and has been one of Florida’s most popular dealer management systems since.

Florida ETR is a member and sponsor of FIADA (Florida Independent Automobile Dealers Association).
